    <section class="section">
        <h2>Business Model</h2>
        <p>Parachute Vault is free and open source for self-hosters, always. Revenue comes from making the experience effortless for people who don't want to run a server, and from add-ons that compose on top of the free core.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Free</strong> &mdash; offline journal + self-hosted vault. No hosting cost on our side.</li>
            <li><strong>$2/mo</strong> &mdash; hosted vault: cloud sync, MCP endpoint, multi-device.</li>
            <li><strong>$5/mo</strong> &mdash; cloud transcription so capture doesn't depend on your laptop being on.</li>
            <li><strong>$10/mo</strong> &mdash; AI reflections and weekly synthesis on top of your vault.</li>
            <li><strong>$100 once</strong> &mdash; the pendant. Always-on voice capture, in development with Marvin Melzer.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We're not competing with anyone's AI subscription. Over 100 million people already pay $20+/mo for AI. Parachute is the $2&ndash;10 add-on that makes whichever one they use dramatically better.</p>
    </section>

