    <section class="section">
        <h2>What We Believe</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Local-first.</strong> Your data lives on your device in a local graph database. If we disappeared tomorrow, your data would still be there&mdash;portable, exportable, entirely yours.</li>
            <li><strong>Voice-first.</strong> Talking is often more natural than typing. We meet people where their thinking actually happens&mdash;on walks, in the car, away from the desk.</li>
            <li><strong>Open source as trust.</strong> The only way to deserve trust with personal thinking is transparency. You can see exactly what the software does.</li>
            <li><strong>AI as partner.</strong> The goal isn't to automate your thinking. It's to help you think more clearly, remember more completely, make connections you might have missed.</li>
            <li><strong>Open standards, not walled gardens.</strong> We build on MCP so your knowledge layer travels with you across every AI you use today and every AI that comes next.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

